				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I actually used coh the other day to pull a named away from his guards because the group I was in lacked paci/harmony puller.
<br />

<br />
The puller was a beastlord. He setup his pet on guard out of agro range of the giants and hit /pet attack targetting one of the escorts. Then he pulled the group using slow on the named. All giants attacked him, but his pet intercepted one escort while I cast coh. He'd dragged the group across the room when CoH landed, clearing agro on him and his pet. Voila! Easy single pulls at 4pp/shot. As a benefit, the named was already preslowed when we pulled him. <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile" border="0" />
