			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">WHAT I would like to see in OoW (and in GoD for that matter):
<br />

<br />
- Raid level quest to implement a portal.
<br />

<br />
For example:  Getting from Qvic to Txevu to Tacvi instance location requires 2 mages to dual CotH which can be very time consuming.  If you don't have at least 2 mages on, it requries a lot of clearing which is even more time consuming.
<br />

<br />
What I would like to see is a raid level quest that requires drops from Noq / Tkarish that the raid leader combines in a container from someone in Abysmal Sea.  The combine may require more exotic items as well such as tradeskill combines, drops from other mobs.  Long story short, you get kind of a key.  Using this key, the leader can create a portal which will send the raid to safe location outside of Tacvi instance.  There could be other restrictions such as Tkarish has to be down, etc.  If SOE is worried about not enough money being taken out of the economy (i.e. pearls) there could be a reagant cost of 5 Blue Diamonds or something to activate as well.
<br />

<br />
We would still have to CotH the stragglers, but our job would be considerably easier.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=653282" target=_blank>Casala</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.hneguild.com" target=_blank>Heaven and Earth</a>
<br />
Saryrn</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
